    <!-- captions -->
    <cbml:panel>
    <cbml:caption xml:id="eg_009" rendition="#uc">Thus, there and then--<lb/> suddenly--uncontrollably--<lb/> the awesome
        <emph>transformation</emph><lb/> starts--until-- </cbml:caption>
    </cbml:panel>
    
    
</div>
            <div>
                <!-- caption -->
<cbml:panel>
    <cbml:caption rendition="#uc">
        <hi rendition="#b">S</hi>lowly the mists begin to clear, as a
        strange, startling world takes form!
        A world in which the impossible is
        believable, and the incredible is
        commonplace--the world of the
        dark domain--the world of the
        dread <emph rendition="#b">Dormammu!</emph>
    </cbml:caption>
    <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#drstrange">
        The journey is over!
        But, judging by the 
        unspeakable menace
        I see before me, the
        <emph rendition="#b">battle</emph> is just begun!
    </cbml:balloon>
</cbml:panel>
